WEBVTT

00:08.840 --> 00:10.719
I am not a spy.

00:10.720 --> 00:12.539
I am a simple fisherman.

00:12.540 --> 00:14.039
I love this country.

00:14.040 --> 00:17.143
No. No. No.

00:17.144 --> 00:19.146
Why didn't you take the medicine?

00:23.359 --> 00:26.027
You ever get the feeling
you're being watched?

00:26.028 --> 00:28.149
Chester, you have to go!

00:28.150 --> 00:29.160
Aah!

00:29.169 --> 00:31.020
[WOMAN SHOUTS]

00:33.410 --> 00:34.577
- [WIND HOWLING]
- What?

00:34.578 --> 00:36.038
[PEOPLE GASP]

00:36.042 --> 00:38.440
What evil?

00:40.050 --> 00:44.779
[FILM PROJECTOR RUNNING]

00:44.780 --> 00:46.279
[MAN PERFORMING DIALOGUE IN JAPANESE]

00:48.000 --> 00:54.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:10.120 --> 01:11.240
[WOMAN NICKERS LIKE A HORSE]

01:20.749 --> 01:23.127
<i>[YOSHIDA'S VOICE URGES]:
Chester, you have to go.</i>

01:25.500 --> 01:28.779
[GUNSHOTS CRACK, YOSHIDA SCREAMS]

01:28.780 --> 01:30.467
[VOICE ECHOING]

01:32.660 --> 01:34.220
[MAN PERFORMING DIALOGUE IN JAPANESE]

01:41.760 --> 01:46.000
[JEEP PASSING]

02:05.900 --> 02:07.504
[URINATING]

02:11.300 --> 02:15.380
[CROWD MURMURING]

02:24.100 --> 02:28.692
[♪♪♪]

02:50.830 --> 02:55.260
[BABY CRYING]

02:57.120 --> 02:59.600
[BACKGROUND CONVERSATIONS IN JAPANESE]

03:03.640 --> 03:07.360
[MURMUR OF MANY VOICES]

03:33.930 --> 03:35.580
Good night.

03:38.750 --> 03:40.050
[WOMEN GIGGLE]

03:49.520 --> 03:54.580
[BABY CRYING]

04:00.380 --> 04:05.440
[♪♪♪]

